and you scare the fish away.

24
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,319  X1:313 X2:404 Y1:484 Y2:510
Oh no.

25
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:58,960  X1:101 X2:617 Y1:484 Y2:510
