I admit them.

27
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:05,509  X1:176 X2:542 Y1:484 Y2:516
As a faint reflex of passion.

28
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:08,960  X1:154 X2:565 Y1:448 Y2:516
