44
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,916  X1:119 X2:600 Y1:448 Y2:516
For you should know
I was too young when I got married.

45
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:13,235  X1:128 X2:591 Y1:484 Y2:510
