54
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:57,789  X1:142 X2:574 Y1:448 Y2:516
I am ready to bet
they are talking about fire-arms.

55
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:05,837  X1:136 X2:584 Y1:447 Y2:516
